## ğŸš€ Installation (Developer Mode)

1. Open Chrome and go to  
   `chrome://extensions`
2. Enable **Developer mode** (top right)
3. Click **Load unpacked**
4. Select the `meow-extension` folder
5. Click anywhere on a webpage â†’ **MEOW ğŸ±**

---

## ğŸ”§ Customization

### Add Your Own Sounds
Replace MP3 files inside the `sounds/` folder  
Keep the same filenames or update them in `content.js`.

### Add More Websites
Edit the `siteMap` object in `content.js`:
```js
const siteMap = {
  "youtube.com": "angry",
  "leetcode.com": "meow2",
  "google.com": "kitten"
};
